metadata.name: Rektography (#1/555)
metadata.description:
VeeFriends Mini Drops Rektography - Created By [VeeFriends](https://veefriends.com) and [OSF](https://www.osf.art/) Rektography is a collection created by artist OSF for the VeeFriends 11th Gift Goat collaboration. There are 12 editions in the collection, totaling 555 tokens. OSF’s style combines hand-drawn elements combined with glitchy, flickering animation. The drawings feature the iconic cameras used by world-renowned photographer Terry O’Neill. The holder of the NFT at the time of the airdrop was gifted an exclusive Iconic Images print of a work created by Terry O’Neill. This was the 11th NFT gifted to Gift Goats and was airdropped on 4/25/2023. This NFT does not grant you previous or future gifts from the Gift Goat Gifting Experience. For more information on the Gift Goat Series, please visit: [https://veefriends.com/giftgoat](https://veefriends.com/giftgoat) OSF [Website](https://www.osf.art/)
